# BiteSpeed Backend Task – Identity Reconciliation

## Overview
This project implements the **Identity Reconciliation service** required in the BiteSpeed backend assignment.

The goal of this service is to **identify and link multiple contact records belonging to the same customer** based on shared **email or phone number**.

Customers may place orders using different emails or phone numbers. This service consolidates those records into one identity.

---

## Live Demo

**Frontend Tester**

